```python
points = []
for i in range(0,len(df)):
    points.append([df['Lat'][i], df['Long'][i]])
    
    folium.Marker([df['Lat'][i], df['Long'][i]], 
                  tooltip=df['Cafeteria'][i],
                  icon=folium.Icon(color='darkblue', icon='coffee', prefix='fa')).add_to(mapa)
    
```

mapa
